      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-quality example of BMW\u2019s finest naturally aspirated era. Powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, the engine features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been meticulously serviced for peak volumetric efficiency. Power is routed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally flawless, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed suspension geometry that maintains original factory kinematics. With concours-level paint depth and an interior free of bolster wear or pixel degradation, this vehicle offers a pure, tactile driving experience for the serious collector.",
